<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/1327681-i-didn-t-get-why-the-aging-thing-was">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[I didn’t get why the aging thing was bothering Ivan. I mean yes, she’ll age while you won’t but he’d still be able to be with her? I mean other couple from other books did the same thing and they went through with it fine?<br />Also it’s implied that she ended up with Benjamin but wasn’t he moving back to NY? <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1327681'><a id="like_count_community_question_1327681" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1327681?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">2 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F158119.If_You_Could_See_Me_Now">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1327681-i-didn-t-get-why-the-aging-thing-was">3 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1327681-i-didn-t-get-why-the-aging-thing-was">See all 2 answers</a>
