        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer601688064" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17522820601504616212">There are some books which makes you happy just like that without any genuine reason behind it, this was one of those for me. I really like this imaginary world of happiness which Cecelia Ahern created and yes it was indeed a modern fairy tale with a practical ending which was actually the best part. Whenever I used to open this book it only took me to another world, a world which I was glad to be a part of.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


