              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13307094951184410511">Will Cecelia Ahern ever not make me cry? Probably not. <br/><br/>This was another beautiful story filled with imagination and joy. I loved it. It was happy and lovely and sad at the same time. It was a lovestory, but then again it wasn&apos;t. It was about loving yourself and accepting yourself and choosing happiness over sadness. This book had a great moral and I can highly recommend it to everyone. This was my fourth Cecelia book and again, it was a definite win. </span>
  <span id="freeText13307094951184410511" style="display:none">Will Cecelia Ahern ever not make me cry? Probably not. <br /><br />This was another beautiful story filled with imagination and joy. I loved it. It was happy and lovely and sad at the same time. It was a lovestory, but then again it wasn't. It was about loving yourself and accepting yourself and choosing happiness over sadness. This book had a great moral and I can highly recommend it to everyone. This was my fourth Cecelia book and again, it was a definite win. </span>
